This is a placeholder for the PvP Kraft (.mcpack) file.
In a real environment, this would be a ZIP-compressed folder containing:
1. manifest.json
2. pack_icon.png
3. textures/items/diamond_sword.png (Shortened)
4. textures/items/gold_apple.png (Vibrant)
5. textures/items/fishing_rod_uncast.png (Minimal)
6. textures/blocks/cobweb.png (Clean)

To make this a real pack:
1. Create a folder with these assets.
2. Zip the contents.
3. Rename the .zip extension to .mcpack.
